ProcurementOfficer_left --> UC_SpecialPR
ProcurementOfficer_left --> UC_ReplenishmentQty
ProcurementOfficer_left --> UC_CriticalPartsDashboard
ProcurementOfficer_left --> UC_LowStockAlerts
ProcurementOfficer_left --> UC_PRNotification

UC_DashboardKPIs <--- ProcurementOfficer_right
UC_StockLevelValuation <--- ProcurementOfficer_right
UC_LowStockCriticalReport <--- ProcurementOfficer_right
UC_StockMovementUsage <--- ProcurementOfficer_right

UC_WorkOrderPartIssuance <-- MaintenanceTechnician_right
